## Protocol.Page.PrintToPDFRequest.ignoreInvalidPageRanges property

Whether to silently ignore invalid but successfully parsed page ranges, such as '3-2'. Defaults to false.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
ignoreInvalidPageRanges?: boolean;
```
